{
  "stem": "628.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "You know, I was what's it called.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I played the-- the-- the strong man.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And you can imagine, I'm not tall now.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I was smaller.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] I had that uniform on with-- with boots, you know, clean.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Every morning, when I came to that gate, I put-- every night, in the barracks, I used to put my trousers under the mattress to put my-- that perfect looking the next day.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Cleaned my teeth-- I went into the cold-- we had the potatoes kitchen there-- cleaned my-- I showered myself with cold water, not to get lice.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So when I came to the gate, my boots, [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "[GERMAN] 875 [INAUDIBLE] reports on the gate.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "You can imagine, I want to see that [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I can imagine, I would have been in their position, this is-- this is unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "After four or five months, I got stronger and stronger.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "The day came-- very, very powerful story, telling that the day came July, August.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I didn't see the other boys.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Sometimes I saw a group.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "They were living in the back, with the Sonderkommando.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And [INAUDIBLE] said, always, he said that later, and I know I gave-- when I saw these boys, I gave them bread.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I was organized.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I was outside.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I helped them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "But in the evening, they were closed into the barracks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "But I-- [SNEEZES]",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the barracks, and I was-- I could walk about.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And no-- nobody came to the front gate.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The day-- Rabetzki was also a bastard.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Rabetzki was the worst one of all.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[SNEEZES]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know if you hear the name-- name.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was Romanian SS.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He got-- he's-- in all the books, he is.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When I look at the books, I said to my wife, this is Rabetzki!",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
